      "Scholarship & Financial Guidance: iExplain assists students in exploring scholarships, education loans, and financial planning, making studying abroad more affordable.",
      "Test Preparation Support: They offer coaching for exams like IELTS, TOEFL, PTE, GRE, and GMAT, helping students meet admission requirements effectively.",
      "End-to-End Support (Pre & Post Admission): Support doesn't stop at admission—iExplain also helps with accommodation, travel planning, forex, SIM cards, and post-arrival assistance."
