      "Expert Career Counselling: Students receive one-on-one counselling sessions to choose the right course and university, like Monash, based on their academic profile, budget, and career aspirations.",
      "Complete Admission Assistance: From university shortlisting to application submission, SOP, LORs, and documentation—iExplain provides full support throughout the admission process.",
      "Visa Processing Support: The consultancy helps students with visa applications, documentation, and interview preparation, reducing stress and increasing approval chances.",
      "Scholarship & Financial Guidance: iExplain assists students in exploring scholarships, education loans, and financial planning, making studying abroad more affordable.",
      "Test Preparation Support: They offer coaching for exams like IELTS, TOEFL, PTE, GRE, and GMAT, helping students meet admission requirements effectively.",
      "End-to-End Support (Pre & Post Admission): Support doesn't stop at admission—iExplain also helps with accommodation, travel planning, forex, SIM cards, and post-arrival assistance."
